{
  "stem": "6719.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was selected once to go to the gas chamber or to be killed, let's put it this way, ah, because I-- I-- I-- I-- came out of having typhoid.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I looked like-- well, I was what they used to call a mussulman.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know, a mussulman was like two sticks instead of legs, and thin, and this and that, and dirty and filthy.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And um, he got me out of it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I'll explain to you later how.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But, uh-- I mean how he did it not, but how it happened.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, one day we-- this was 19-- 1943.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Latter part of '43, I got typhoid, and I was in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was [SIGHS] you know, what they used to call the K-- KB, Krankenbau.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Everything in, in the-- the camp was abbreviated-- Krankenbau.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Strafkompanie was SK.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was all abbreviations.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And uh-- a lot of my friends that knew me, that I worked with, that used to work in Kanada, used to bribe somebody on there to hide me underneath a bunk, uh, when there was a selection on.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There usually was one or two selections a week of people that-- you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And everybody stood straight up and said, well, I, Ich bin Gesund.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They looked like death warmed over.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So anyhow, I got out of this and, uh, and I, uh-- out of the-- out of the hospital.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And, uh, I worked in a place where I could sleep during the day under a big table that, uh, people sat around, uh, maybe, uh, uh, five, six meters in diameter.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I slept there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that's how I got my strength back, but I still looked awful.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
